div.div: Sekai Saikou no Ansatsusha, Isekai Kizoku ni Tensei suru
Action, Adventure, Drama, Fantasy, Mystery, Romance

The world's number one assassin has been reincarnated as the eldest son of a family of aristocrat assassins. In exchange for being reincarnated in another world, a goddess has imposed upon him one condition. "Kill the Hero who is prophesied to destroy the world."
This was to be the mission in his new life. The synergistic effect of the vast knowledge and experience he gained that made all manner of assassinations possible in the modern world, and the secret techniques and magic of the fantasy world's most powerful family of assassins turn him into the greatest assassin of all time.
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Senpai ga Uzai Kouhai no Hanashi

Being seen as a full-fledged business woman isn’t easy for Futaba Igarashi when her senpai, Harumi, treats her like a kid. Days for her are never typical, at work or outside of it, with all the antics going on in her life. As mishaps ensue, she’ll find herself growing closer with her loudmouth senpai. Maybe Futaba feels more than she lets on, but one thing’s for sure: she’s still annoyed!
(Source: Funimation)
Kono Sankaku Love Come wa Shiawase ni Naru Gime ga Aru.

"What do you like about Reira so much?"

Tenma Yashiro, an ordinary high school boy, accidentally discovers that Rinka, a cool beauty in his class, is in love with his childhood friend, Reira Tsubaki, a beautiful and innocent girl. Tenma then helps Rinka become friends with Reira, but...

"If Yashiro-kun isn't dating Rinka-chan, then can I be your girlfriend instead?"

"What did you do, Yashiro?"

So Reira falls in love with Tenma, and a love triangle develops between him and the two most beautiful girls in school. What will happen in this complicated love story?

Winner of the 28th Dengeki Novel Award Gold Prize! The happiest love triangle in the history of romantic comedy begins!

(Source: Dengeki Bunko, translated)
